{"tid":1044040,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"希治閣恐怖電影仲有無參考價值？","createTime":"2019-03-02T15:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T06:09:27.000Z","uid":59014,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"89c7aa133077b1a977c84ca857f98f20fa3fbcf0","tid":1044040,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:53:53.000Z","msg":"而加既恐怖片慣左jump scare 同 bloody scene <br />\n好多時會係某個場景 空間度製造恐怖然後講故事，然後又係一個場景制造恐怖<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日睇返d戲 psycho , rear window , 迷魂記 , the bird 發現主要營造係懸念感 角色心理 自玄其說上面<br />\n懸念貫切到尾到最後開估  呢個世代睇返唔覺得太恐怖"},{"pid":"f4b8c6402ab0befbd09a0400392d26cd973c08e0","tid":1044040,"uid":77788,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:59:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06ecfa819e2b83d3a865825a00e0d7c049053269","tid":1044040,"uid":59014,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f4b8c6402ab0befbd09a0400392d26cd973c08e0","tid":1044040,"uid":77788,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:59:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:01:24.000Z","msg":"恐怖 驚悚 懸疑 任你Up 啦"},{"pid":"844a50b57d44127564cb2b206b6c265adbb8e2e8","tid":1044040,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:02:41.000Z","msg":"睇過rear window同vertigo, 講真唔識欣賞"},{"pid":"4c19401b3a20611ad74d0f326e719d00386cf44d","tid":1044040,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:03:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2562c667d15ee6da52b173a0f3787c4cf01f8ff7","tid":1044040,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"佈局"},{"pid":"f42bbc87a3c21df053e1351fa8d3a9c8784abe9e","tid":1044040,"uid":4855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:08:35.000Z","msg":"呢種恐怖係陰暗面 精神上嘅恐怖"},{"pid":"b05de338aca2312c2c55b6abaeb305bffb0a340d","tid":1044040,"uid":59014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"844a50b57d44127564cb2b206b6c265adbb8e2e8",